x Make index.html with textbox and button
x In index.html, we made fake comments with <p>
x Make server.js with express.static('public')

. In server.js, add app.get('/api/hello') which does res.send('hello!')
  . Try it out: Go to localhost:4002/api/hello
. In server.js, add app.get('/api/messages') which does res.send(["message1", "message2"])
. In your frontend (index.html, script.js), fetch('/api/messages') and display it in place of the fake comments

. Add app.post('/api/messages') using a variable (Use that variable for app.get('/api/messages') too)

. Replace the variable stuff with database stuff
